From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Filip Pokryvka <fpokryvk@redhat.com>
Date: Thu, 10 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0200
Subject: [PATCH] net: netdevsim: Support changing carrier state

Add ndo_change_carrier callback and ethtool get_link to netdevsim so
that carrier state can be toggled via "ip link set dev <name> carrier
on|off" and properly detected by network management daemons.

The get_link ethtool op is needed so that NetworkManager recognizes
the device as supporting carrier detection (CAPABILITIES.CARRIER-DETECT).
Without it, NM ignores carrier state changes regardless of the
ignore-carrier configuration.

This is needed for NetworkManager CI to test the ignore-carrier device
configuration option with match-device=mac against netdevsim devices
that support permanent addresses.

Signed-off-by: Filip Pokryvka <fpokryvk@redhat.com>
---
 drivers/net/netdevsim/ethtool.c | 1 +
 drivers/net/netdevsim/netdev.c  | 12 ++++++++++++
 2 files changed, 13 insertions(+)

diff --git a/drivers/net/netdevsim/ethtool.c b/drivers/net/netdevsim/ethtool.c
--- a/drivers/net/netdevsim/ethtool.c
+++ b/drivers/net/netdevsim/ethtool.c
@@ -171,6 +171,7 @@ static const struct ethtool_ops nsim_ethtool_ops = {
 	.supported_coalesce_params	= ETHTOOL_COALESCE_ALL_PARAMS,
 	.supported_ring_params		= ETHTOOL_RING_USE_TCP_DATA_SPLIT |
 					  ETHTOOL_RING_USE_HDS_THRS,
+	.get_link			= ethtool_op_get_link,
 	.get_pause_stats	        = nsim_get_pause_stats,
 	.get_pauseparam		        = nsim_get_pauseparam,
 	.set_pauseparam		        = nsim_set_pauseparam,
diff --git a/drivers/net/netdevsim/netdev.c b/drivers/net/netdevsim/netdev.c
--- a/drivers/net/netdevsim/netdev.c
+++ b/drivers/net/netdevsim/netdev.c
@@ -493,6 +493,16 @@ static int nsim_stop(struct net_device *dev)
 	return 0;
 }
 
+static int nsim_change_carrier(struct net_device *dev, bool new_carrier)
+{
+	if (new_carrier)
+		netif_carrier_on(dev);
+	else
+		netif_carrier_off(dev);
+
+	return 0;
+}
+
 static int nsim_shaper_set(struct net_shaper_binding *binding,
 			   const struct net_shaper *shaper,
 			   struct netlink_ext_ack *extack)
@@ -553,6 +563,7 @@ static const struct net_device_ops nsim_netdev_ops = {
 	.ndo_bpf		= nsim_bpf,
 	.ndo_open		= nsim_open,
 	.ndo_stop		= nsim_stop,
+	.ndo_change_carrier	= nsim_change_carrier,
 	.net_shaper_ops		= &nsim_shaper_ops,
 };
 
